short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sort problems based on solved count

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is useful for https://cses.fi/problemset/.
This rearranges tasks in descending order of solved count. That makes it easier for user to solve in order of increasing difficulty of tasks.

You can see it working in the example screenshots.
